quran[8]{c,v,t}:
  11,46,"(Katonda) naagamba nti owange Nuhu mazima yye si wa mu bantubo mazima yye yakola ekikolwa ekitali kirungi, n'olwekyo tonsaba ekyo kyotalinaako kumanya, mazima nze nkubuulirira oleme kubeera mu batategeera"
  11,47,(Nuhu) naagamba nti nkusaba obukuumibwo nneme kuba nga nkusaba ekyo kye sirinaako kumanya era bwotonsonyiwe n'onsaasira nja kubeera mu bafaafaaganiddwa
  11,48,"Newalangirirwa nti owange Nuhu kka (ove mu lyato), ebiva gye tuli, gibe mirembe na mikisa ku ggwe, ne ku bibiina bya bantu ebiri naawe ne ku bibiina bya bantu betujja okweyagaza mu nsi, oluvanyuma ebibonerezo ebiruma ennyo bibatuukeko okuva gye tuli"
  11,49,"Ebyo bye bimu ku bintu ebyekusifu tubikutumira ggwe (Muhammad) tobimanyangako ggwe wadde abantubo oluberyeberye lwa kino, n'olwekyo gumiikiriza, mazima enkomerero (e nnungi) y’abatya Katonda"
  11,50,"Era ab'ekika kya A’di twabatumira muganda waabwe Hudu naagamba nti abange abantu bange musinze Katonda, ngoggyeko yye tewali kirala kyonna kisinzibwa, temuli mmwe okugyako abagunja obugunja bye musinza"
  11,51,"Abange bantu bange, si basaba mpeera ku kino, empeera yange teri okugyako ku oyo eyantonda, abaffe temutegeera"
  11,52,"Era abange bantu bange, mwegayirire Mukama omulabirizi wa mmwe, oluvanyuma mwenenye mudde gyali, ajja kubasindikira okuva mu bire waggulu enkuba etonnya ngeddingana, era abongere amaanyi ku maanyi ga mmwe, era temukyukanga nemuva ku ekyo ne muba aboonoonyi"
  11,53,"Nebagamba nti owange ggwe Hudu totuleetedde bujulizi bweyolefu (ku ebyo byogamba) ate era naffe tetuyinza kuleka ba katonda baffe olw'okuba ogambye, era ffe tetugenda kukukkiriza"